SUMMARY:Again\, but Different - MFA Thesis Dance Concert
LOCATION:1920 7th Ave. Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:A thesis dance concert constructed from everyday actions\, ges
 tures\, and task-based movement\, organized through choreographic tools an
 d principles. Drawing on early 1960s postmodern minimalism\, the work trea
 ts ordinary behavior as both compositional material and a pedagogical stra
 tegy. In turn\, it broadens what we recognize as dance\, offering access b
 eyond codified technique and widening participation regardless of technica
 l training or ability. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/179581
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/179581
END:VEVENT
