SUMMARY:CAMPGround26 Concert 2
LOCATION:1624 E 7th Ave Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:CAMPGround26\, an international new music festival\, takes ove
 r Tampa\, FL\, March 57! Expect multiple world premieres\, three brand-new
  monodramas\, and a special house installation projectall packed into an u
 nforgettable first week of March. Dont miss this one-of-a-kind musical adv
 enture! This noon concert showcases a vibrant range of styles\, sounds\, a
 nd aesthetics in new solo and ensemble music\, including two new works by 
 Youshin Gim and John Liberatore written for the CAMP ensemble. Stop by at 
 noon to experience inspiring artworks at Tempus Projects alongside an afte
 rnoon of great music. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/185891
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/185891
END:VEVENT
