SUMMARY:Walking Tour: Ybor City
LOCATION:1303 E 8th Ave Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:Step back in time to the cigar capital of the world. Ybor City
 s rich cultural heritage and immigrant roots made it one of Floridas most 
 vibrant communities. Tour Tampas only National Historic Landmark District 
 and learn about early Ybor City people\, social life and work culture. Str
 oll past mutual aid societies\, the Ybor Cigar Factory and other key landm
 arks. Each tour runs 90 minutes and kicks off at 10 a.m. With only 25 spot
 s available\, youll enjoy an intimate experience as you explore about one 
 mile of Tampas historic sidewalks and brick streets. Wear your most comfor
 table walking shoes and dress for the weatheryoull want to enjoy every ste
 p. Tour Details Meeting Place: Jose Marti Park at the Corner of 8th Ave an
 d 13th St\, Tampa\, FL Tickets: Advance tickets required. Private tours ca
 n be arranged by calling (813) 228-0097 Dont miss your chance to walk the 
 streets where history was made. Claim your ticket now and join us for an u
 nforgettable journey through Ybor City. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.g
 ov/node/185836
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/185836
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
