SUMMARY:Morgan Street Quick Build Public Meeting
LOCATION:720 E. Zack St. Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Youre invited to a public meeting on Wednesday\, March 25th fr
 om 6-8 PM at the Tampa Firefighters Museum (720 E. Zack St.) to learn all 
 about the planned Morgan Street Quick Build. This project will use the exc
 ess space on Morgan St to build separated bike lanes from Brorein St to Ha
 rrison St on the west side of the road. The roadway will be resurfaced\, a
 nd new signs and pavement markings installed. Parking and necessary travel
  lanes will be maintained. This project will make Morgan St safer and more
