LOCATION:11602 Westchase Golf Dr. Tampa \, FL 33626 United States
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to tee it high and let it fly at the Inaugural Semin
 ole Scramble Golf Tournament! The Tampa Bay Seminole Club is thrilled to b
 ring Nole Nation together for a day of friendly competition and Seminole s
 pirit\, all in support of full-ride scholarships for Tampa Bay students. J
 oin us at Westchase Golf Club on March 28 for a fun-filled day on the gree
 n. Whether youre swinging with friends\, family\, or colleagues\, this scr
 amble-style tournament promises great golf and unforgettable memories. You
 r participation directly supports future Seminoles: every dollar raised he
 lps send local students to Florida State University on scholarship. What t
 o Expect: A beautifully manicured course perfect for all skill levels Shot
 gun start at 8:30 AM Prizes\, raffles\, and a silent auction Refreshments 
 throughout the day Lunch and an awards ceremony to wrap up the fun Event A
 genda: 7:308:15 AM: Check-In Silent AuctionRaffles Open 8:158:20 AM: Natio
 nal Anthem 8:208:25 AM: Tournament Overview Rules 8:30 AM: Shotgun Start 1
 2:30 PM: Lunch Awards Ceremony Dont miss your chance to hit the green for 
 a great cause. Grab your foursome\, mark your calendars\, and join us for 
 a day thats all about community\, competition\, and cheering on the Garnet
  Gold. Go Noles! \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/177156
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/177156
