SUMMARY:Walk For Wishes Tampa
LOCATION:1701 N Highland Ave Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:The 13th Annual Walk for Wishes Tampa will take place on Satur
 day\, April 11\, 2026. Lace up your shoes and join us for a heartwarming d
 ay of fitness and fun at Water Works Park! For additional event details\, 
 please visit walkforwishestampa.org. Walk For Wishes is a feel-good event 
 that everyone from student groups to large companies can participate in an
 d make a difference in the lives of local children and families. Since the
  events inception\, over 15\,000 supporters have made wishes come true one
  step at a time. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/179586
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/179586
