 d by those impacted by substance use. Attendees will gain insights into tr
 auma-informed approaches\, community resources\, and effective communicati
 on techniques that promote hope and connection. Together\, we can make a d
 ifference. Presented by Bay Care and UHC Onsite Nurse Liaison. This webina
