SUMMARY:A Night with Mary Lee039\\\;s House: Viva Havana!
LOCATION:1910 N Ola Ave\, Tampa\, FL 33602 Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Step into the spirit of Havana for an unforgettable evening de
 dicated to changing childrens and families lives in Hillsborough County! O
